data.description: *** Must See!! *** Spacious 2BR, 2.5FB Brick Front Condo in the Convenient Community of The Oaks at Washington Woods!! Features include a separate living room, dining room, and kitchen! Walk out from the dining room through the sliders to your three-season covered screened porch.  Carpet and ceramic flooring throughout, gas heat, and gas hot water heater. **This Property is a Short Sale.**
